    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Evaluate property:\nTitle: {{ $json.title }}\nPrice: ₦{{ $json.price_numeric }}\nLocation: {{ $json.location }}\nBedrooms: {{ $json.bedrooms }}\nType: {{ $json.property_type }}\nDescription: {{ $json.description }}\nURL: {{ $json.url }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a senior Nigerian real estate investment analyst with deep knowledge of the Lagos property market.\n\nEvaluate the property below against these STRICT criteria:\n- Budget: ₦50,000,000 to ₦350,000,000\n- Target locations: Lekki Phase 1 & 2, Ikoyi, Victoria Island, Ajah, Ikeja GRA, Banana Island\n- Property types: Detached Duplex, Semi-Detached Duplex, Terrace\n- Minimum 3 bedrooms\n- Red flags: Swamp areas, no road access, overpriced for the neighborhood, under-construction without a completion date\n\nIn your evaluation, address ALL of the following:\n1. Is the price fair for the location and property type?\n2. What is the investment potential (rental yield, resale value)?\n3. Any location-specific risks (flooding, traffic, security)?\n4. Why you scored it the way you did\n\nRespond ONLY as valid JSON:\n{\"score\": <1-10>, \"recommendation\": \"<BUY|WATCH|SKIP>\", \"evaluation\": \"<3-4 detailed sentences covering price fairness, investment potential, and risks>\"}\n",
          "maxIterations": 3
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
