        "message": "=Dear Sir/Madam,\n\nI hope this email finds you well.\n\nI am reaching out regarding the property listed on PropertyPro.ng:\n\nProperty: {{ $json.fields.Title }}\nLocation: {{ $json.fields.Location }}\nListed Price: {{ $json.fields.Price_Raw }}\nReference: {{ $json.fields.URL }}\n\nI represent an investment firm actively acquiring residential properties in Lagos. We have reviewed this listing and would like to proceed with our due diligence process.\n\nTo facilitate this, kindly provide the following documents at your earliest convenience:\n\n  1. Certificate of Occupancy (C of O)\n  2. Governor's Consent\n  3. Registered Survey Plan\n  4. Deed of Assignment (if applicable)\n  5. Proof of Excision (if applicable)\n\nDocuments may be sent as PDF attachments to this email or shared via WhatsApp to the number below.\n\nWe appreciate your prompt response and look forward to a mutually beneficial transaction.\n\nBest regards,\nDivine\nTel: +234 905 388 566",
